-- Peugeot Citroen, Changan to Invest $1.2 Billion in Chinese Joint Venture
-- Laurence Frost
-- 2010-07-09T08:30:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-09/peugeot-citroen-changan-to-invest-1-2-billion-in-chinese-joint-venture.html

          
          
             PSA Peugeot Citroen and China Changan
Automotive Group Co. said they will invest 935 million euros in
their joint venture to be signed in Paris today.  
          
          


  


        